column1: Baby Barnaby's////I had the Annie's burrito
column3: fit my "diet"/clean eating plan perfectly!  My boyfriend had the migas with chorizo and he might as well have licked his plate clean.  Our server was a little rushed playing hostess as well
column4: but she kept up nicely.  I love that they leave a pot of coffee and carafe of water at your table
column5: don't have to wait for much besides your food once you get seated!
